 operations throughout the world and our commitment to both the environment and the communities in which we operate hunt oil company is an industry leader in the exploration and production business and other energyrelated areas over time we have grown to be one of the largest independent oil and gas companies in the world our primary focus is earlystage exploration opportunities emphasizing idea and prospect generation establishment of land positions and efficient use of cuttingedge technologies our growth vision includes expanding into new geographies as well as exploring and developing newer unconventional oil and gas projects we also have deep experience in lng project development and operations hunt is the lead shareholder and operator of the peru lng project in peru and a shareholder in the yemen lng project in yemen hunt oil company celebrated its th anniversary in  since  one of our strengths has been to employ extraordinarily talented and motivated people we strive to provide an exceptional work environment in which our employees contributions and ideas are both recognized and valued our organizational structure is lean and efficient empowering decisionmaking throughout all levels of our company believing in the power of our people remains a vital element to our companys continued success and longevity we encourage you to browse our website read about our exciting business and learn more about what we do youll find that we are in many ways unique with philosophies that combine oldfashioned principles with modern thinking and technology it is this varied mix of virtue and ingenuity that will enable us to continue fulfilling our vision to be a growthoriented industry leader for many years to come sincerelysteve suellentroppresidenthunt oil company about steve suellentrop selected representatives mark gunnin chief operating officer dennis grindinger executive vice president south america paul habenicht executive vice president north america karim abuhamad senio